Hi there, my name is Kath!
I'm an avid milkshake drinker, an aspiring kaleidoscope collector, and a visual storyteller.


I'm also a dedicated college student who strives to find creativity in the crevices of everyday life while combining it with optimism to find solutions. I'm currently a senior at Saint Joseph's University in Philadelphia, PA, studying English and Communication Studies. I like making and designing things, both big and small. Words and images work well together to create memorable stories and they are what inspire me. On this website, you will find my current digital projects that I've worked on inside and outside of the classroom, as well as writing, music, and other artsy stuff that I'm currently working on.
